Assignment: Given two lists, list_1 and list_2, create a new list
named diff_list that contains all the elements from list_1 that are not in
list_2. Make sure there are no duplicates in diff_list, and use the sort
function to arrange it in ascending order.

diff_list = []

for item in range(len(list_1)):
    if list_1[item] not in list_2 and list_1[item] not in diff_list:
        diff_list.append(list_1[item])

diff_list.sort()
